&lt;p&gt;官网 https://nginx.org -&amp;gt; 点击 download -&amp;gt; 点击 Pre-Built Packages-&amp;gt; 点击 stable and mainline -&amp;gt; 选择系统 RHEL and derivatives&lt;/p&gt;
